Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: New Card Is Being Produced
body: On April 23, 2021, we ordered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190092979, and will mail it to the address you gave us. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Picked Up By The United States Postal Service
body: On April 23, 2021, the Post Office picked up mail containing your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190092980. We mailed your card to the address you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708405762556. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you did not receive the card, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we resend the card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
